  "body": "This PR contains the following updates:\n\n| Package | Type | Update | Change | References |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| eslint-import-resolver-webpack | devDependencies | minor | [`0.10.1` -> `0.11.1`](https://diff.intrinsic.com/eslint-import-resolver-webpack/0.10.1/0.11.1) | [source](https://togithub.com/benmosher/eslint-plugin-import) |\n\n---\n\n### Release Notes\n\n<details>\n<summary>benmosher/eslint-plugin-import</summary>\n\n### [`v0.11.0`](https://togithub.com/benmosher/eslint-plugin-import/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md#&#8203;0110---2015-11-27)\n\n[Compare Source](https://togithub.com/benmosher/eslint-plugin-import/compare/v0.10.1...v0.11.0)\n\n##### Added\n\n-   Resolver plugins. Now the linter can read Webpack config, properly follow\n    aliases and ignore externals, dismisses inline loaders, etc. etc.!\n\n</details>\n\n---\n\n### Renovate configuration\n\n:date: **Schedule**: \"every weekend\" in timezone Europe/Paris.\n\n:vertical_traffic_light: **Automerge**: Enabled.\n\n:recycle: **Rebasing**: Whenever PR is stale, or if you modify the PR title to begin with \"`rebase!`\".\n\n:no_bell: **Ignore**: Close this PR and you won't be reminded about this update again.\n\n---\n\n - [ ] <!-- renovate-rebase -->If you want to rebase/retry this PR, check this box\n\n---\n\nThis PR has been generated by [Renovate Bot](https://togithub.com/marketplace/renovate). View repository job log [here](https://renovatebot.com/dashboard#algolia/instantsearch.js).",
